  <h1 class="gem-c-title__text gem-c-title__text--long">
    EU exit, universities, research and innovation: stakeholder working group
  </h1>
</div>
  </div>
  

  <div class="govuk-grid-column-two-thirds">
    
  <p class="gem-c-lead-paragraph ">
    Terms of reference and membership for the group, which discusses research and innovation policy in the light of the UK’s exit from the EU.
  </p>

  </div>
</div>

